    "biography": "<p>A small, sly Awakened black cat (Felis nigra) that holds strong territorial ideas and toys with intruders using its mind-affecting powers. Sometimes kept as a (dangerous) pet.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Accident (LOS), Adaptive Coloration, Blindness (LOS), Compulsion (LOS), Darkness, Desire Reflection (LOS), Enhanced Movement, Enhanced Reactions (for [Essence]D6 turns, 1D6 times/day), Enhanced Senses (Low-Light Vision), Hypnotic Howl (miaow, Zone ×2), Illusion (LOS)</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Catnip (acts as a powerful intoxicant — see book)</p><p><em>Attacks: 6L, Reach −1 (claws). Habitat: Woodland, heaths, rocky hills, fringes of urban areas. Range: Throughout Europe, especially the U.K. and east-central Europe. 3D6 Initiative dice. Book Intelligence 3/8. PAE p.19.</em></p>",
